timeline.bodyText:
Similar to @nik9000's comment, it looks like source will be loaded twice here for cases when a script needs to access  _source and when _source is requested for hits because we will have two different SourceLookup objects , for example for queries like this:
{
  "_source": true,
  "query": {
    "match_all": {}
  },
  "script_fields": {
    "my_script": {
      "script": {
        "source": "params['_source']['my_field']"
      }
    }
  }
}

